{"title":"VGI-2025","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Cardiología/Cardio Enfermedades de la aorta.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Enfermedades de la Aorta","guid":"P0d2Nvy2QiOJosEF6ajPjg","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"FISIOPATOLOGIA GENERAL","guid":"QOfZM_fLRpS7ksbBzo_7zg","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Aneurisma verdadero","guid":"DNlx8YOlRHetfEbtudWfqg","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"Dilatacion de las 3 capas (intima, media, adventicia)","guid":"OukTuqenSKSsIb81B-O7jA","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"Tunica media → contiene musculo liso + fibras elasticas","guid":"IB17J89URoeQLwHGRgxYhQ","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"2","text":"Alteracion → degradacion de elastina y colágeno → ↑ colágeno → pérdida distensibilidad","guid":"Z9ggnt0iSIWLuI7hnwf5jg","children":[]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"Seudoaneurisma (falso)","guid":"lB_oGKy_SruswaFGLyaB6Q","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"Ruptura de intima y media → contenido por adventicia y tejido periaortico","guid":"O_xgBFWqSteVB4m2R3_XqQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"1","text":"Aneurisma disecante → ver Sindrome Aortico Agudo","guid":"zrgBWw3kRemF3XxnGZuGkQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"0","text":"ANEURISMA AORTICO","guid":"NhqisOmfR0--9J-7RhFRkQ","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"Definicion","guid":"L4kPd_eBQg-aovgjbOh3YA","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"Dilatacion focal permanente >50% del diametro esperado por edad y sexo","guid":"lFi54xUeSjCOU823NGnCnA","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"Ao ascendente: >45 mm (o >40 mm con Marfan/valvula bicuspide)","guid":"khPmHUbmQOa7-JmbavgGWQ","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"10","text":"Ao abdominal (AAA): >30 mm (normal <20 mm)","guid":"aTusgfqfREes3vnKq0v6vQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"9","text":"EPIDEMIOLOGIA","guid":"XXOwgSC4Ti6cBMtTY2ej5A","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14