osis avanzada","guid":"TPx67lOeT0OLzKsBTvwmNg","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"81","text":"Enfermedad genetica del tejido conectivo","guid":"SCWqKHNyS-uxVulp-lMT7A","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"Marfan, Loeys-Dietz, Ehlers-Danlos vascular","guid":"DbgJgquSQTaanm2D1CF_mQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"86","parent":"81","text":"Aorta bicuspide → riesgo elevado","guid":"w6M7k1C2SDSn1C7qXtuiKQ","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"81","text":"Traumatica (accidente, ciclista, deporte de contacto)","guid":"69fd9JvaRXqG_LXTsJXutQ","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"81","text":"Iatrogena (post-cateterismo, post-TAVI, post-cirugia)","guid":"HxfoQ07vQrWKC1TTyWwhUw","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"81","text":"Enfermedad de Erdheim (necrosis quistica de la media)","guid":"nKlYw3GoQJuwmL_USx6Cww","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"59","text":"CLASIFICACION","guid":"55IdMs-kTNeBuLGXRC4Nrw","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"Stanford A → compromete Ao ascendente (independiente de donde comienza)","guid":"IbFSxaR4T8SX5UlWlCvqzQ","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"EMERGENCIA QUIRURGICA inmediata","guid":"vZLrwxXpT0uu9ixljufOlA","children":[]}]},{"id":"93","parent":"90","text":"Stanford B → solo Ao descendente (distal a Ao subclavia izq)","guid":"stRn45XWRXycdBN7Qq-afg","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"B no complicada → manejo medico","guid":"KFqDtnGxQlWfgflq2Q9GNg","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"93","text":"B complicada → TEVAR endovascular","guid":"SPcKeR5pT5iW_H9LTS2Q_Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"90","text":"DeBakey (historica)","guid":"ZhMwQXFPSzOSQdYvPc1K3w","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"Tipo I: Ao ascendente + descendente","guid":"tBRaoV3TQ4qKzKPI2XtjXA","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"96","text":"Tipo II: solo Ao ascendente","guid":"oBZTII3JR2anYS7FR5ISYw","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"96","text":"Tipo III: solo Ao descendente","guid":"JPNdM6FmSdCp3grk-n0cMQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":