agica)","guid":"FbIVA078Q6GPXNeCE-ICPQ","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"Alternativa si TC no disponible o inestable","guid":"lYntI-XpQkOdC5me8DZaSw","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"132","text":"Evaluacion valvula aortica e insuficiencia aortica en tipo A","guid":"WeeEch2MQnqxyMHOh4lDvQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"135","parent":"125","text":"RNM → si duda diagnostica y paciente estable (lento, menos accesible)","guid":"zB0nBV7YTEuQAfNbHIMssg","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"125","text":"Aortografia → gold standard historico, NO primera linea","guid":"qXCLnOKdTbWsFWggNFc0EQ","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"125","text":"Eco transtorácica: limitada pero util (ventana pericardica, insuficiencia aortica)","guid":"d709sjSARqWf1aXiMljuRA","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"125","text":"LABORATORIO","guid":"HDYaO89-T32Gy0injDUXaw","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"Troponina (IAM asociado), hemograma, funcion renal, grupo + prueba cruzada","guid":"HOLMe1iOQ5m-jcrKPXwQYw","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"138","text":"D-dimero: valor negativo ayuda a descartar (alta sensibilidad, baja especificidad)","guid":"71EZacr9Rqy_g9QryePlxA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"141","parent":"59","text":"TRATAMIENTO","guid":"GfTPapybTPCvTLPO4WT8ng","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"CONTROL SHEAR STRESS (OBJETIVO INMEDIATO)","guid":"pyYa_-fERQ-CTiF9Gs3yPg","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"PAS 100-120 mmHg (o <120 mmHg)","guid":"GyE9WGr2QQqA61sxZVGAXQ","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"142","text":"FC 60-80 lpm","guid":"JfkWcY7uTKyPpm4F5oVlQg","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"142","text":"BETABLOQUEADOR EV de primera linea","guid":"yEu4jQ8AT4yDfN5ca_ZQHQ","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"Labetalol (alfa + beta) → de eleccion","guid":"7BlXC2TESuujAXOQX00ypg","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"145","text":"Esmolol (vida media corta, titulable)","guid":"m-TWOkDmTdC1gTI7IamMHg","children":[]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"142","text":"BCC EV si contraindicacion a BB (asmatico)","guid":"nkPCWIJZSSuK6NwzfOfA9g","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"Verapamilo, diltiazem","guid":"7Kth-Qs8SzOsr2u0tMzNgg","children":[]}]},{"id":"150","parent":"142","text":"Vasodilatadores si PAS >120 post-BB","guid":"s_KvD2BHQGWUILhO5n2N5A","children":[{"id":"151","parent":"150","text":"Nitroprusiato (cuidado taquicardia refleja)","guid":"2O_51cQhQKe0_3ANuBrmOw","children":[]}]},{"id":"152","parent":"142","text":"ANALGESIA","guid":"sc-JTZ0mT3O8hh3k0eqyWg","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"Morfina → reduce tono simpatico + dolor","guid":"OPfAgCtTSeKrIy99p_Uvmg","children":[]}]},{"id":"154","parent":"142","text":"NO EMPLEAR ANTICOAGULANTES (en diseccion aguda)","guid":"DqhMxa02SQmaTlMUlpNm6A","children":[]}]},{"id":"155","parent":"141","text":"TIPO A → CIRUGIA DE EMERGENCIA","guid":"-fl2ppK7TeyxahJMmLigsA","children":[{"id":"156","parent":"155","text":"Reemplazo Ao ascendente","guid":"SJ83ujwCQz6sbVMbUXS9hA","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"155","text":"Reparacion valvula aortica si insuficiencia significativa","guid":"SVeTT-xHQsmmrtXl3amkcQ","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"155","text":"Mortalidad quirurgica 10-20% (mayor en AM)","guid":"TFD0QmrNS0asNIp0FiSrPQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"159","parent":"141","text":"TIPO B NO COMPLICADA → MANEJO MEDICO","guid":"MWND4FpHSGm-ZKE5tjudJQ","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"Control estricto PA (objetivo <135/80 cronica)","guid":"85y5ysONRlSee7Qb00R9vQ","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"159","text":"BB oral de preferencia","guid":"Ew72teQlSQO0pQxU7Io2bQ","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"159","text":"Control con TAC a 1, 2, 12 meses → luego anual","guid":"n2hKjJrzRWm45gU7XbqtgA","children":[]}]},{"id":"163","parent":"141","text":"TIPO B COMPLICADA → TEVAR (endovascular)","guid":"SZ3ln1wPRpKjxPH-t8ZCHw","children":[{"id":"164","parent":"163","text":"Indicaciones","guid":"jBtggcdNTvqR5MjcATp-MQ","children":[{"id":"165","parent":"164","text":"Dolor intratable a pesar de tratamiento medico","guid":"8sjViC3oR-GCCiV7KtLxcQ","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"164","text":"Progresion diseccion (↑ grosor pared, VAP diametro >20mm, profundidad >10mm)","guid":"caX_hSp0Rii4_rOdH25K-A","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"164","text":"Hematoma intramural (HI) con progresion","guid":"r-NZsloCQ3upEXIqROeQbw","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"164","text":"Sangre extraadventicial","guid":"1TOG_I9OSueMnUydoh0hLg","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"164","text":"Aumento derrame pleural","guid":"ahZjVQwjR-yWiptQkXR-TA","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"164","text":"Sindrome mala perfusion","guid":"VuhSMgUWTn6-la2CuPXE2g","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"164","text":"Compromiso ostium de vasos viscerales","guid":"uIOSlnROTuyDSbUhAEzxPA","children":[]}]},{"id":"172","parent":"163","text":"TEVAR ahora preferido sobre cirugia abierta en tipo B complicada (ESC 2024)","guid":"k8KCN8PNQL-TI9dmqYrzEg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"173","parent":"59","text":"SEGUIMIENTO POST-DISECCION","guid":"mG_nzT0YT2CffsfJT9Xkcg","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"TAC a 1 mes, 2 meses, 12 meses → luego anual","guid":"ymAif-Y8RRuz4Zs9bXYMew","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"Control estricto de FRCV (PA, tabaquismo, lipidos)","guid":"qIeqw4jxRPKP_0eBgT-BXA","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"173","text":"No ejercicio isometrico","guid":"0rlIY7l4S_Cj7alHnjLBDw","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"173","text":"Evitar trauma toracico","guid":"Xb-sf4dJRymzQoz-G576Vg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"178","parent":"0","text":"CONSIDERACIONES GERIATRICAS","guid":"90C8BaOaSPa_Q7GKY3fkqA","children":[{"id":"179","parent":"178","text":"Aneurisma aortico en AM","guid":"XH77TN-WTyapyzZgF5tUQw","children":[{"id":"180","parent":"179","text":"Mayor prevalencia de AAA en >65 anos tabaquistas","guid":"068pJoISSDedvizJfdng1A","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"179","text":"Presentacion: mayoria asintomatica descubierta por imagen (eco abd, TC)","guid":"W4L-F6mFQYiln_e6d8JkUQ","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"179","text":"Screening: eco abdominal x1 en hombres 65-75 anos fumadores (USPSTF)","guid":"MVfg3kWNQfONfqWib-6NPg","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"179","text":"Umbral Qx igual que adulto no AM, pero EVALUAR FRAGILIDAD antes de decision","guid":"BlPqZeFaRDK_VcHdRJlM3g","children":[]}]},{"id":"184","parent":"178","text":"Diseccion aortica en AM","guid":"5NuieSAiQQ2i4SCyQRehsA","children":[{"id":"185","parent":"184","text":"Mayoria Stanford A en >70 anos por aterosclerosis y HTA cronica","guid":"sP_RiD0TRIqDYy4NbD8wlw","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"184","text":"Mortalidad quirurgica MAYOR en AM (>70 anos: mortalidad tipo A 25-30%)","guid":"83EWFDQHSGe0c-zdm_xCYA","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"184","text":"Discutir proporcionalidad terapeutica en AM fragil con tipo A","guid":"99QDQ4H-SZ-I5jSg2FppMQ","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"184","text":"Tipo B complicada: TEVAR tolerable incluso en AM fragil (menos invasivo que cirugia)","guid":"6-nfy2X8QEiuNK_R5uzBWw","children":[]}]},{"id":"189","parent":"178","text":"Presentacion atipica en AM","guid":"N4CfbWGBSs61PeYttSy1fQ","children":[{"id":"190","parent":"189","text":"Dolor menos intenso o atipico (puede simularse como dolor musculoesqueletico)","guid":"On24dNnHS7OjmRKrb83qGQ","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"189","text":"Mareo, sincope, confusion pueden ser la presentacion principal","guid":"F0u8f_SoRomVFp2p0LiV6g","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"189","text":"Diferencia de PA entre brazos → clave diagnostica no debe ignorarse en AM","guid":"nVxZFr3MSvO6BycUJTIKQw","children":[]}]},{"id":"193","parent":"178","text":"Postoperatorio","guid":"bFG1Pu-JSJKi1NGLw_pugA","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"Mayor riesgo delirium, insuficiencia renal, prolongacion estancia","guid":"D7PBOUVGSD2eSuMOXIyl7g","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"193","text":"Evaluacion CFS preoperatoria en cirugias electivas","guid":"uc1On2W_QUmCv8CeJglI3w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"196","parent":"0","text":"VER TAMBIEN","guid":"1KHvDJdaQSSv6-b-HrBqEQ","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"→ Sindrome coronario agudo (Cardiologia)","guid":"r_Odmr12QIScDdTBPuTBQQ","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"196","text":"→ Taponamiento cardiaco (Cardiologia)","guid":"20x_RVOPRMSmvMt7sfZ_SA","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"196","text":"→ HTA manejo general (Cardiologia)","guid":"qRPsKgj7Q9CyV0-_h-HtHA","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"196","text":"→ Sindrome de Marfan (Genetica)","guid":"5l_h_tfIQo6tZ1H5IbGSdw","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"196","text":"→ Shock cardiogenico (Cuidados Criticos)","guid":"t8vXp1iCR8WrCleN3ySQYQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"202","parent":"0","text":"PERLAS CLINICAS","guid":"6U-WvBepROakjJaQPSSE4A","children":[{"id":"203","parent":"202","text":"DOLOR TORACO-DORSAL BRUSCO + DIFERENCIA PA ENTRE BRAZOS → diseccion hasta descartar","guid":"DP550Q59QWmyVZqWndJ0zA","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"202","text":"D-DIMERO negativo tiene alta VPN para descartar SAA (pero no reemplaza imagen)","guid":"HlO8esM1Q5u9HjQ8FvIV7A","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"202","text":"Nunca anticoagular diseccion aguda → aumenta mortalidad","guid":"3jXmQ9KtQjmk_fTpwalBvA","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"202","text":"Tipo A → CIRUGIA EMERGENTE (mortalidad 1-2%/hora sin cirugía)","guid":"pbrh1y_LSCy75SSBqWR_RA","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"202","text":"Tipo B complicada → TEVAR de primera eleccion segun ESC 2024","guid":"MHoWriIGQouFmis2v0GezA","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"202","text":"Mujeres con AAA: mayor riesgo de rotura a menor diametro → umbral quirurgico 50 mm","guid":"OhkAi1b_R-W9aeCr02B_2Q","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"202","text":"En Marfan: BB + losartan (combinar ambos) → enlentecen dilatacion aortica","guid":"uaGyPwQTQaKDIFYbbVVnjg","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"202","text":"Post-TAVI u otro procedimiento + dolor: descartar diseccion iatrogena","guid":"RUq5jG2mSLq4S2KVQXP7vg","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"202","text":"AM con tipo A: discutir proporcionalidad → mortalidad quirurgica 25-30% en >70 anos","guid":"5aJN2aiyQX-6p7NLG_8Xvw","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"202","text":"Coartacion de aorta en adulto no diagnosticado: diferencia PA >20 mmHg brazos vs piernas","guid":"gffLSkXfR3-9JN9g_My00A","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"202","text":"REFERENCIAS","guid":"hQS58CqgT46RENAPC4nfxw","children":[{"id":"214","parent":"213","text":"1. Erbel R, et al. 2014 ESC Guidelines on the diagnosis and treatment of aortic diseases. Eur Heart J. 2014;35(41):2873-2926.","guid":"WSONhWj8SiWcGtp9oXaafQ","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"213","text":"2. Isselbacher EM, et al. 2022 ACC/AHA Guideline for the Diagnosis and Management of Aortic Disease. JACC. 2022;80(24):e223-e393.","guid":"rA99TUSeR9agwxKjDDOfVw","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"213","text":"3. Mussa FF, et al. Acute Aortic Dissection and Intramural Hematoma: A Systematic Review. JAMA. 2016;316(7):754-763.","guid":"XiwElPcMSU2tLqBicXo-jQ","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"213","text":"4. Golledge J, Eagle KA. Acute aortic dissection. Lancet. 2008;372(9632):55-66.","guid":"7uCxF7cmQvufAMOTECLccA","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"213","text":"5. Oderich GS, et al. Society for Vascular Surgery TEVAR guidelines. J Vasc Surg. 2021;73(1):5S-28S.","guid":"8zyPdx1uQ3OIlI5xeD4Neg","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":218,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Estudios Pivotales","folder":"Estudios Pivotales","filename":"VGI-2025","id":"map_181","resolved_references":[]}